<br>
As far as Total Domination, this is really only useful for soloing.  The addition of a non dire charmed mob to a group is not as useful considering bad charm breaks compared to the DPS it adds.  If you are going to be soloing a lot then Total Domination is worth it.  Seems to add about 20 to 30% to the average charm duration although you will still get charms that instantly break sometimes.<br>
<br>
Gather mana is a nice one though and should probably be bought before rune. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><br>
