<br>
-  Werewolf - Not boon of the garou, actual WW illusion adds a great deal of STR and pure ATK.  Stacks with NDT right now as well.<br>
-  Fire Elemental - DS<br>
-  Air Elemental - componentless lev<br>
-  Water Elemental - Componentless EB<br>
-  Drybone - Fire resist<br>
-  DE - Ultravision<br>
-  Gnome - Shrink<br>
-  Various racial illusions - Factions to do quests<br>
<br>
So it does have some uses.  In general though, you're right, it's mostly for fun and other AA are more useful.  Still, you play this game for fun, right? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><br>
